thread.title: Kayla Hockett
thread.title_full: StorPlace Self Storage reviewed by Kayla Hockett

author: Kayla Hockett
title: Kayla Hockett
text: Our lease was up on our apartment and our house want finished yet it would be a week maybe a week in a half until we would have our keys. I called and luckily got a unit the ladies were WONDERFUL. They took my payment got us moved in we ended up not needing the unit as long as we thought. They worked with us understanding the circumstances. I will highly recommend this location to everyone I know!!!! If I could give 10 stars I would.
